## Widget Integration

### JavaScript Widget

Include the widget script on your website:

```html
<script src="https://your-sting-domain.com:8092/widget/bot-widget.js"></script>
```

Initialize the widget:

```javascript
STINGChat.init({
  apiKey: 'sk_your-api-key',
